body:
This no longer builds with `verilator --cc --top top bug.sv`:
```
package pkg;
    function automatic bit fn(int value);
    endfunction
endpackage

interface ifc();
    localparam int PARAM = 1;
endinterface

module mod(ifc i);
    localparam bit lpbit = pkg::fn(i.PARAM);
endmodule

module top();
    ifc i();
    mod m(.i);
endmodule
```
failing with:
```
%Error: Internal Error: bug.sv:11:33: ../V3Task.cpp:1557: func ref not under scope
   11 |     localparam bit lpbit = pkg::fn(i.PARAM);
      |                                 ^~
                        ... See the manual at https://verilator.org/verilator_doc.html?v=5.047 for more assistance.
```

This worked and started failing with commit 5821d069 (#7128)

